<section class="home-section">
  <h1 class="home-section__title">Welcome to Your Inventory App!</h1>

  <p class="home-section__intro">
    This app helps you keep track of your items by organizing them into clear
    categories.
  </p>

  <section class="getting-started">
    <h2 class="getting-started__title">How to Use</h2>
    <ul class="getting-started__steps">
      <li class="getting-started__step">
        Create custom categories like <em>Electronics</em>, <em>Clothing</em>,
        or <em>Tools</em>.
      </li>
      <li class="getting-started__step">
        Add items under each category (for example: Laptop, Jacket, Hammer).
      </li>
      <li class="getting-started__step">
        Easily view, update, or remove items as needed.
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <p class="home-section__note">
    <strong>Note:</strong> Some built-in categories and items cannot be edited
    or deleted.
  </p>
</section>
